Non-negotiable rules:

1. Never expose service_role to frontend.
2. All tables must have RLS policies.
3. All state transitions must use RPC or Edge functions.
4. Tier-4 data must stay inside secure schema.
5. All sensitive actions must create audit logs.
6. No destructive migrations.
7. Follow API_CONTRACTS response format.
8. Follow DEPLOYMENT_SOP for environment separation.

